## Technical Specifications

- Data Models
  - NarrativeEvent schema (expanded)
    - id: UUID
    - source_platform: string
    - speaker_entity: string
    - speaker_role: string
    - audience_class: string
    - raw_text: string
    - event_time: timestamp
    - ingested_at: timestamp
    - created_at: timestamp
    - provenance: JSON (source_url, citation)
    - signals: JSON (array of SignalRecord or embedded)
    - credibility_score: float
    - risk_score: float
  - SignalRecord
    - id: UUID
    - narrative_id: UUID
    - type: string (enum: management_language_consistency, repetition_consistency, negative_earnings_language, legal_governance_words, etc.)
    - description: string
    - weight: float (0–1)
    - source: string
    - detected_at: timestamp
